{"kanda":6,"sarga":42,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"ततस्तेराक्षसास्तत्रगत्वारावणमन्दिरम् ।न्यवेदयन्पुरींरुद्धांरामेणसहवानरैः","trans":"Then the Rakshasas proceeding to Ravana's abode informed that Rama along with the vanaras have occupied the whole of Lanka.","words":[{"d":"तत","m":"then"},{"d":"राक्षसा","m":"Rakshasas"},{"d":"स्तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"रावणमन्दिरम्","m":"Ravana's abode"},{"d":"गत्वा","m":"proceeding to"},{"d":"रामेण","m":"Rama's"},{"d":"वानरैः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सह","m":"along with"},{"d":"रुद्धां","m":"occupied"},{"d":"न्यवेदय","m":"informed"},{"d":"न्पुरीं","m":"total city."}]},{"v":2,"dev":"रुद्धांतुनगरींश्रुत्वाजातक्रोधोनिशाचरः ।विधानंद्विगुणंश्रुत्वाप्रासादंसोऽध्यरोहत","trans":"On knowing that Lanka is occupied, the night ranger Ravana, became very furious and doubled the forces of Lanka for the protection and went to the top of Lanka palace.","words":[{"d":"रुद्धां","m":"occupied"},{"d":"तु","m":"also"},{"d":"नगरीं","m":"city"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"जातक्रोधो","m":"very furious"},{"d":"निशाचरः","m":"night ranger"},{"d":"विधानं","m":"knowing"},{"d":"द्विगुणं","m":"twice"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"प्रासादं","m":"top of the mansion"},{"d":"अध्यरोहत","m":"planning for the protection of Lanka."}]},{"v":3,"dev":"सददर्शावृतांलङ्कांसशैलवनकाननाम् ।असङ्ख्येयैर्हरिगणैःसर्वतोयुद्धकाङ्क्षिभिः","trans":"He observed a countless number of Vanara troops spread all over Lanka, mountains, and forests.","words":[{"d":"स:","m":"he"},{"d":"युद्धकाङ्क्षिभिः","m":"desirous of combat"},{"d":"असङ्ख्येयै","m":"countless numbers"},{"d":"हर्रिगणैः","m":"troops of Vanaras"},{"d":"सशैलवनकाननाम्","m":"mountains and forests"},{"d":"सर्वतो","m":"all over"},{"d":"अवृतां","m":"occupied"},{"d":"लङ्कां","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"ददर्शा","m":"observed."}]},{"v":4,"dev":"सदृष्ट्वावानरैःसर्वांवसुधांकवलीकृताम् ।कथंक्षपयितव्याःस्युरितिचिन्तापरोऽभवत्","trans":"Seeing the Vanaras occupying the entire earth, Ravana thought of destroying and started thinking.","words":[{"d":"स:","m":"he"},{"d":"वानरैः","m":"Vanaras"},{"d":"सर्वां","m":"all"},{"d":"वसुधां","m":"earth"},{"d":"कवलीकृताम्","m":"occupied"},{"d":"दृष्ट्वा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"कथं","m":"how"},{"d":"स्युरिति","m":"thought"},{"d":"क्षपयितव्याः","m":"to destroy"},{"d":"चिन्तापरो","m":"thinking"},{"d":"अभवत्","m":"started."}]},{"v":5,"dev":"सचिन्तयित्वासुचिरंधैर्यमालम्ब्यरावणः ।राघवंहरियूथांश्चददर्शायतलोचनः","trans":"Ravana, thinking over for long, picking up courage, saw Rama's Vanaras with thoughtful eyes.","words":[{"d":"स:","m":"he"},{"d":"रावणः","m":"Ravana"},{"d":"सुचिरं","m":"for long"},{"d":"चिन्तयित्वा","m":"thinking over"},{"d":"धैर्यमालम्ब्य","m":"picking up courage"},{"d":"अयतलोचनः","m":"with thoughtful eyes"},{"d":"राघवं","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"हरियूथांश्च","m":"at the Vanaras"},{"d":"ददर्शा","m":"saw."}]},{"v":6,"dev":"राघवःसहसैन्येनमुदितोनामपुप्लुवे ।लङ्कांददर्शगुप्तांवैसर्वतोराक्षसैर्वृताम्","trans":"Raghava accompanied by the army happily went near and witnessed Lanka filled with Rakshasas all over.","words":[{"d":"राघवः","m":"Raghava"},{"d":"मुदितो","m":"happily"},{"d":"सहसैन्येन","m":"with army"},{"d":"पुप्लुवे","m":"near"},{"d":"लङ्कां","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"सर्वतो","m":"all over"},{"d":"राक्षसैर्वृताम्","m":"fully filled with Rakshasas"},{"d":"गुप्तांवै","m":"protected"},{"d":"लङ्कां","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"ददर्श","m":"witnessed."}]},{"v":7,"dev":"दृष्ट्वादाशरथिर्लङ्कांचित्रध्वजपताकिनीम् ।जगामसहसासीतांदूयमानेनचेतसा","trans":"The son of Dasaratha saw Lanka decorated with flags and posts and thinking of Sita he became very worried.","words":[{"d":"दाशरथि","m":"son of Dasaratha"},{"d":"चित्रध्वजपताकिनीम्","m":"decorated with flags and posts"},{"d":"लङ्कां","m":"Lanka"},{"d":"चेतसा","m":"thinking"},{"d":"सीतां","m":"of Sita"},{"d":"दूयमानेन","m":"worried"},{"d":"सहसा","m":"very much"},{"d":"जगाम","m":"remained."}]},{"v":8,"dev":"अत्रसामृगशावाक्षीमत्कृतेजनकात्मजा ।पीड्यतेशोकसन्तप्ताकृशास्थण्डिलशायिनी","trans":"\"Here (Lanka) is the daughter of Janaka, i